data.description: Contract Pending Move-in ready Raised Ranch with great updates! Fully fenced backyard with wood privacy fence, patio, and a great space for a firepit or pool. A/C new in 2020. Renovated Kitchen with stainless steel appliances, gas stove, tile backsplash, board & batten walls, pantry/storage. Washer & Dryer included! Wood floors & Ceiling Fans in Bedrooms and Great Room. Newly finished basement with Rec Room, Bonus Room and Storage/Utility Room. Double wide driveway for extra parking. Charming location close to park, trail, and swimming pool. Motivated Seller.
